data.name: textBox3.Text
data.value: 1) 75% hostel attendance is mandatory . 2) All the hostelers must enter before 8 pm. 3) No electric appliances are allowed in hostel premises. 4) Tobaco, ciggerate, alcohol are prohibited. 5) Maintain full decipline in the hostel. 6) Any loss to the hostel property shall be paid by the hostelers involved.
